      title: "What fails first during leader flapping?",
      level: "advanced",
      tags: ["failure first", "leader election", "fencing"],
      prompt: "A scheduler leader pauses under GC, loses its lease, resumes, and repeatedly competes with a new leader. Duplicate job dispatch and database conflicts appear.",
